title: RUSSIA MUST HOLD - Red Orchestra 2 Gameplay {Multiplayer}
description:
Red Orchestra 2 Gameplay - Shermanator and I fight as Russia to hold back the German Advance!  This is a fun battle that goes on for awhile.  I am not the best at this game, but I really enjoy it!  And I had a lot of fun with Sherman!  Enjoy the Battle :D

Check out Sherman's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/TheGameGuards

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
